.background_2#_about_press
  .container
    .row.centered
      %h3.ouishare_stencil.white
        = t('dynamic_translations.press.title')
      %hr.white
      %br

    #myCarousel.carousel.slide.col-xs-12.col-md-offset-1.col-lg-offset-2.col-md-10.col-lg-8{ 'data-ride' => "carousel"}

      /Wrapper for slides
      .carousel-inner
        .item.active
          .press-content
            .press-text
              %h3.naiv
                “For anyone under the impression that the rise of the sharing economy is simply a blip reaction to the recession, the OuiShare conference is proving otherwise”
          .label-press
            The Guardian
        .item
          .press-content
            .press-text
              %h3.naiv
                This year’s theme, the Age of Communities, was broad enough to welcome all sides of the movement: venture capitalists alongside black markets, slow foodies alongside Bitcoin promoters.
          .label-press
            Al Jazeera
        .item
          .press-content
            .press-text
              %h3.naiv
                “Parmi les trois points sensibles évoqués à l'occasion du OuiShareFest: le rapport aux institutions, la possibilité de participer à la réduction des inégalités, et la durabilité du modèle collaboratif”
          .label-press
            Le Monde
        .item
          .press-content
            .press-text
              %h3.naiv
                \...este festival sin orden pero con sentido..
          .label-press
            El Pais
        .item
          .press-content
            .press-text
              %h3.naiv
                The atmosphere was positive and driven. This was an assembly of doers, creators, and thinkers.
          .label-press
            Shareable

      %img.quote-left-carousel{:src => '/assets/quote_left.png', :alt => 'quote left'}
      %img.quote-right-carousel{:src => '/assets/quote_left.png', :alt => 'quote right'}
      / Controls
      %a.left.carousel-control{:href => "#myCarousel", 'data-slide' => "prev"}
        &lsaquo;

      %a.right.carousel-control{:href => "#myCarousel", 'data-slide' => "next" }
        &rsaquo;



